Intro
------ 
 
Syntax
------- 
 Simply place the following syntax into the page markup: 

 <code>
  ====== Rater ======
  For simple votings by thumgs up/down:  
  {(rater>id=1|name=item1|type=vote)}    
  
  For 5 star rating:  
  {(rater>id=1|name=item1|type=vote)} 
 </code>


Installation
------------
 Just download and extract it as folder “rater” into your “\lib\plugins” 
 directory.


